Made this for my husband's and his father's birthday party, and it was a huge hit. I think the subtle sweetness is an asset. For kids you might want something more sugary but the adults here loved it. (Crystalized ginger can be expensive in the little jars so buy in bulk when you can find it- try penzeys.com.)

