Rating: 3
This cake is delicious. I serve it with cinnamon ice cream. It's easy to make-just mix a generous amount of cinnamon in vanilla bean ice cream-stir until creamy and smooth and refreeze for a couple of hours. It's a great complement. I always get many happy reviews from my guests and requests for the recipe.

